# EventDetailActions(event)
- IF: ${ event.isOrganizer }
    - ```
    {
        "type": "ActionSet",
        "actions": [
            ${UpdateEventAction(event)},
            ${CancelEventAction(event)}
        ]
    }
    ```
- ELSEIF: ${event.response == 'notResponded'} 
    - ```
        {
        "type": "ActionSet",
        "actions": [
            ${RespondAcceptAction(event)},
            ${RespondDeclineAction(event)}
        ]
    }
    ```
- ELSE: 
    - ```
        {
        "type": "ActionSet",
        "actions": [
            ${RespondDeclineAction(event)}
        ]
    }
    ```

